    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 0,
      "text": "This paper present extensions of the Self-Attention Generative Adversarial Network approach SAGAN, leading to impressive images generations conditioned on imagenet classes.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "text": "The key components of the approach are :",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_heading",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "text": "- increasing the batch size by a factor 8",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "text": "- augmenting the width of the networks by 50%",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "text": "These first two elements result in an Inception score (IS) boost from 52 to 93.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "text": "- the use of shared embeddings for the class conditioned batch norm layers, orthonormal regularization and hierarchical latent space bring an additional boost of IS 99.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "text": "The core novel element of the paper is the truncation trick: At train time, the input z is sampled from a normal distribution but at test time, a truncated normal distribution is used: when the magnitude of elements of z are above a certain threshold, they are re-sampled.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "text": "Variations of this threshold lead to variations in FD and IS, as shown in insightful experiments.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "text": "The comments that more data helps (internal dataset experiments) is also informative.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "text": "Very nice to have included negative results and detailed parameter sweeps.",
      "suffix": "\n\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "SJl68_Hx37",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "text": "This is a very nice work with impressive results, a great progress achievement in the field of image generation.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_evaluative",
      "fine_review_action": "none",
      "aspect": "asp_motivation-impact",
      "polarity": "pol_positive"
    },
    {
